{"tid":1505133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"偽勇武\"可唔可以退翻去二三線(長文希望你地睇曬佢)","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:05:33.000Z","uid":272788,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc0847b3f0c83443f7d4157a91e493c6a7b988d","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:55:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>每次都要同前線講，都講到口臭。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你冇心理準備比人拉，去犧牲唔好係前線拎光環打飛機。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而你企得係前線，你就要有救手足，打狗嘅決心。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成日對家都未黎射幾粒蛋啲人就縮，大佬呀，對而一隻狗都冇，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">重點係我地有roadblock 架</span></span>。好多次都係咁，已經睇得出好多人都係有裝無勇。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成日一有速龍，個個頭也不回就向後跑</span></span>，屌你田徑一百米要跑贏身邊啲手足呀。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">都係嗰句，你企得最前，你就望住正面望住啲警犬走，見到手足比狗捉就幫;唔想冒險比人拉就去翻二三線或者做和理飛，唔好睇小呢件事，因為你一個唔做嘢嘅人係前線塞住，係直接影響手足救唔救到人，會唔會比人拉。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後講一講，都要多謝驚都後到最前嘅手足，你地同狗對峙咁耐，都好有心。<br />\n而二三線下次真係企鬆啲，留多啲位比前線走呀，同埋見好多人拎曬架餐係後面，不如你地下次試下比前線手足，因為好多人都係空手上陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/25/205446_aa3e1d020dddf78425a681e3a5bfcf7c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F25%2F205446_aa3e1d020dddf78425a681e3a5bfcf7c.jpeg&h=e1612923&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb004d02918b4d71b2347a537a139c4948a44c89","tid":1505133,"uid":109124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662184c630d26db9172424f1537e5dcaabb985c0","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"P牌無力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc15c4f5f8f8dfe33cd8e6d4ede8b2bea28200e5","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"手足幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ad515253e600bd9b5f93d96fcd624828338f24","tid":1505133,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"推！唔好死守，比時間對方增援"},{"pid":"f583713e3da9c287bde522cd9d0bf7017d35f21f","tid":1505133,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600509cf186392a6f00400ee0e17a86bc0f48f5","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"次次都要係前線同人講briefing 咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664649a2bdf5c6ea189457793d9a8f1e3185cc6c","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"Share出去呀，二三線並不可恥，你地都好有用，更要和理飛配合。"},{"pid":"23ae4943b877851dfbead372dcf3af4e17f94744","tid":1505133,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"講左好多次企疏預位走，塞撚實哂唔知做乜鳩，搞到前面走唔切俾人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643f4b60731498287a6f2e4594165615fa7f78a4","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:00:49.000Z","msg":"P牌係咁唔應該開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8453d141a32f31b1bf064d24fc3f8363c822652b","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ad515253e600bd9b5f93d96fcd624828338f24","tid":1505133,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"推！唔好死守，比時間對方增援"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"係，一係就組一班肯衝嘅手足，打游擊，見對家少人就上。be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870d13967cbedab2c44ff4892b0dc42bdcce36a8","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ae4943b877851dfbead372dcf3af4e17f94744","tid":1505133,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"講左好多次企疏預位走，塞撚實哂唔知做乜鳩，搞到前面走唔切俾人搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"係，成日望轉頭有好多人以為冇死，點知一放tear gas 個個頭也不回塞住咁走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23fd130330a8b22f58bc044e1f59ce4c59db319","tid":1505133,"uid":272788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb004d02918b4d71b2347a537a139c4948a44c89","tid":1505133,"uid":109124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}